high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the stove where the toaster is.
Pick up the spatula that is on the right side of the toaster.
With the spatula in your hand turn to your left and move in front of the stove.
Open the top drawer that is to the left of the stove while holding the spatula.  Place the spatula in the drawer in the front left.  Close the drawer.
Go to the side of the counter that is to the left of the stove where the spatula is.
Pick up the spatula that is on the counter.
With the spatula in your hand turn and go to the stove but face to the left so the stove is on your right.
Open the drawer that is to the left of the stove with the spatula in your hand.  Place the spatula in your hand in the drawer behind the spatula that is in there. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas away in a drawer.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left at the counter
Pick up the spatula on the counter
Turn right, go forward to the end of the counter
Put the spatula in the drawer
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn right, go forward a bit, turn right and face the counter
Pick up the spatula on the counter
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward a bit, turn around
Put the spatula in the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas in the drawer

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Turn and go to the drawer by the stove.
Put the spatula in the drawer by the stove.
Turn left and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Turn and go to the drawer by the stove.
Put the spatula in the drawer by the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas in the drawer by the stove.
